content.text:
About App Center
For Partners and Developers
Go to App Center
Expand Your App’s Reach
Introduce your app to extensive global marketing audience. Join Semrush App Center.
Become a partner
Tech Guide
Design Guide
Semrush App Center is the go-to spot for marketers looking for best-in-class marketing solutions.
Our marketplace opens up access to Semrush users eager to discover great marketing tools. Our technical teams are dedicated to providing seamless integration of your service with the App Center.
And it doesn’t stop there. We offer full support every step of the way — from app launch and purchase to billing and customer care.
One platform.
All the perks. No hassle.
Audience Growth
Take your app global with access to Semrush’s audience of marketing professionals. Semrush App Center allows you to sell directly to Semrush users without facing any extra costs and with us taking care of the billing process.
Full product support
From product strategy to technical assistance, our dedicated support teams will ensure a seamless app integration process so that users can use your app right within the Semrush interface.
Strategy & marketing support
Semrush takes care of everything — from providing strategic marketing advice on app pricing to defining the optimal marketing mix. We will actively promote your app across our key channels and deliver full customer support.
Become a partner
Meet your audience
Let’s face it — user acquisition is expensive and you’ll have to exhaust some budgets chasing and finding your audience.
Semrush has extensive global network of marketing professionals and now you have the chance to bring your app in front of millions of new users who trust the Semrush quality-check extended to your app.
marketing professionals have already used Semrush
of Fortune 500 companies use Semrush as their go-to tool
Become a partner
Semrush App Center
is just good business
With Semrush’s app store, we provide our solutions to a global digital marketer customer base - without having to deal with go-to-market! The Semrush team provides excellent support in technical integration, customer service and marketing.
Matthias Funk
CPO Co-Founder Tubics
Video Rank Tracker
We’re amazed at how easy and fast it is to develop an app for the Semrush App Center. The team was very helpful in the development and documentation. Plus, we’re able to reach a very high-quality user segment for our app: Mobile App Insights.
Mustafa Buyukkara
Head of Product at MobileAction
Mobile App Insights
Semrush App Center gives an amazing opportunity to extend our customer base and reach a new audience. We are happy with the partnership and moving forward with building new products for the App Center.
Sergey Yakovlev,
CEO Iteora
E-commerce Keywords Analytics
With the App Center, Semrush gave marketers the ability to use dedicated tools for specific marketing tasks. As an App Center partner, we really enjoy working with dedicated professionals that understand their user-base needs. The level of insight Semrush gives us really helps in improving our app and allows us to add great features as our app usage grows.
Alessandro Stigliani
CEO Abyssale
Instant Banner Generator
Grow your app’s visibility together with Semrush App Center
Press the button below to fill in the Semrush App Center partnership request form and showcase your app to the large audience of new users.
Become a partner
Once you submit your partnership request, we will review your pitch within 7 days and get back to you with further details.
If you have any questions or need additional information about becoming a Semrush App Center Partner, don’t hesitate to contact us at app-center@semrush.com.
